      "content": "The Operational Hub (OH) acts as the administrative core of the SNO, handling contributor relationships, compliance, and payment processing. By leveraging legal structures like Swiss Associations, the OH ensures contributors are protected from liability while enabling the SNO to interact with banks, vendors, and regulatory entities. It simplifies tax reporting, cross-border compliance, and contributor agreements.",
